        "Target": "Hunt a Rathalos and Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "\u00C7a sent le roussi !",
        "Client": "Yomogi la chef",
        "Description": "Des dango-lapins cuits lentement\r\nsur la lave... J\u0027en salive rien\r\nque d\u0027y penser. J\u0027allais essayer\r\naux Cavernes de lave quand j\u0027ai\r\nappris qu\u0027un \u003CCOL RED\u003ERathalos\u003C/COL\u003E et\r\nle \u003CCOL RED\u003EMagnamalo\u003C/COL\u003E \u00E9taient dans les parages.\r\nTu pourrais t\u0027occuper d\u0027eux ?",
